le updates) Added a release notes entry if the change is significant</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\"> (Module addition) Added a release notes entry if adding a new NixOS module</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" checked=\"\"> Fits <a href=\"https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">CONTRIBUTING.md</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Add a üëç <a href=\"https://github.blog/2016-03-10-add-reactions-to-pull-requests-issues-and-comments/\" rel=\"nofollow\">reaction</a> to <a href=\"https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/pulls?q=is%3Aopen+sort%3Areactions-%2B1-desc\">pull requests you find important</a>.</p>",
            "url": "https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/pull/307484",
            "title": "ncurses: 6.4 -> 6.5",
            "date_modified": "2024-05-20T21:07:21.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-04-28T14:51:13.000Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "trofi",
                "url": "https://github.com/trofi"
